OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer faces the biggest
OL,8,Fleadership crisis of his premiership
OL,9,Fas Cabinet ministers including the
OL,10,FHome Secretary reportedly urged him to
OL,11,Fconsider his position and Government
OL,12,Faides quit their posts.
OL,14,FShabana Mahmood is said to have
OL,15,Fprivately called for an orderly
OL,16,Ftransition of power on Monday night as
OL,17,F75 out of Labour's 403 MPs demanded
OL,18,Fthe Prime Minister stand down after
OL,19,Fthe party's electoral mauling last
OL,20,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FFour Government aides quit their posts
OL,8,Fciting a loss of confidence in his
OL,9,Fleadership while others warned his
OL,10,Fauthority was collapsing and called
OL,11,Ffor him to set out a timetable for his
OL,12,Fdeparture from No 10.
OL,14,FSir Keir faces an extraordinary weekly
OL,15,FCabinet meeting on Tuesday morning,
OL,16,Fwith senior ministers split over how
OL,17,Fbest to move forward and concerns
OL,18,Famong some about plunging the party
OL,19,Finto a potential leadership contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FThe Press Association understands
OL,8,FDefence Secretary John Healey's
OL,9,Fmessage to Sir Keir was that he wanted
OL,10,Fa chaotic process to be avoided and
OL,11,Ffor the Government to focus on getting
OL,12,Fthe country through the looming risk
OL,13,Fof geopolitical and economic crises
OL,14,Frather than turning inwards.
OL,16,FIn a sign of the febrile atmosphere in
OL,17,FWestminster on Monday evening, junior
OL,18,Fhealth minister Stephen Kinnock said
OL,19,Fsome Cabinet members "may well" call
OL,20,Ffor the Prime Minister to go at
OL,21,FTuesday's meeting.
OL,26,@{D@VOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,F"It is possible that members of the
OL,8,FCabinet might do that. I genuinely
OL,9,Fhave no idea at all. What I am simply
OL,10,Fsaying is any one of my colleagues who
OL,11,Fis potentially thinking of doing that,
OL,12,FI just hope they really will take a
OL,13,Fbeat, pause and reflect, and think
OL,14,Fabout the potential that has for the
OL,15,Fchaos that might be unleashed," he
OL,16,Ftold BBC Newsnight.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
