CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FThe Guardian reported that Ms Mahmood
OL,8,Fand Foreign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,9,Fhad both spoken with the Prime
OL,10,FMinister about his future, while the
OL,11,FTimes reported a third Cabinet
OL,12,Fminister had also told Sir Keir to
OL,13,Fconsider his position.
OL,15,FSpeculation about the Prime Minister's
OL,16,Ffuture has intensified since
OL,17,FThursday's elections, in which Labour
OL,18,Flost almost 1,500 English councillors,
OL,19,Fwent backwards in Scotland and slumped
OL,20,Fto third place in Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
