PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FIn a speech in central London on
OL,8,FMonday, Sir Keir said he took
OL,9,F"responsibility" for the losses but
OL,10,Fwould fight on and cast the current
OL,11,Fpolitical moment as a "battle for the
OL,12,Fsoul" of the UK, warning that if
OL,13,FLabour failed, the country would head
OL,14,Fdown "a very dark path".
OL,16,FThe Prime Minister is expected to meet
OL,17,Fapprentices on Tuesday to talk up the
OL,18,FGovernment's reforms to the system
OL,19,Faimed at helping small businesses take
OL,20,Fon young apprentices, with training
OL,21,Ffully funded from August.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]sD@WOUtD@EO]vD@FOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FThe visit is a bid to highlight his
OL,8,Fpromise to tear up the "status quo"
OL,9,Fwhich he said on Monday had failed
OL,10,FBritish people and underline efforts
OL,11,Fto put apprenticeships on an equal
OL,12,Ffooting with university degrees.
OL,14,FA handful of backbenchers spoke up in
OL,15,Fsupport of the Prime Minister
OL,16,Ffollowing the speech, with
OL,17,FMacclesfield MP Mr Roca and Gedling's
OL,18,FMr Payne saying Sir Keir had
OL,19,Fdemonstrated he understood "the scale
OL,20,Fof the challenge" facing the country.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@cO]{D@\OU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
