OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FMr Streeting, who is widely seen as a
OL,8,Fpotential leadership contender but has
OL,9,Fpublicly denied plans for a tilt at
OL,10,Fthe top job, was understood not to
OL,11,Fhave spoken to Sir Keir as of Monday
OL,12,Fevening.
OL,14,FBut the resignation of his PPS, who
OL,15,Fcalled for a "swift" timetable to
OL,16,Freplace the Prime Minister, and others
OL,17,Fseen as Streeting allies such as Ms
OL,18,FWard, who urged a "rapid process" to
OL,19,Ffind a new leader, have fuelled
OL,20,Fspeculation that he is gearing up to
OL,21,Frun in any contest.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@TO]zD@SOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778547792
OL,3,CStarmer leadership in peril as
OL,4,C'Cabinet ministers tell him to
OL,5,Cconsider position'
OL,7,FIn contrast, supporters of Greater
OL,8,FManchester Mayor Andy Burnham, who is
OL,9,Fseen as a party favourite to replace
OL,10,FSir Keir, are wary of a quick
OL,11,Fleadership election because he would
OL,12,Fneed to fight and win a by-election to
OL,13,Fbecome an MP first in order to further
OL,14,Fhis own ambitions.
OL,16,FIn a speech to the Communication
OL,17,FWorkers Union on Monday, former deputy
OL,18,Fprime minister Angela Rayner ` herself
OL,19,Fregarded as a potential leadership
OL,20,Fcontender ` said the decision to block
OL,21,FMr Burnham should be "put right".
OL,26,@}D@VOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
